        //- floating text on right
        .service-text-fixed#innovation
          h1 Innovation strategy
          p We'll unpack your idea and align our teams to the problem you're solving and the solution needed to create and test it quickly.  Together, we'll consider all possibilities, both good and bad. We'll look at the short-term launch and validation of your product alongside the long-term business opportunity and growth plan. 
        .service-text-fixed#prototyping
          h1 Concept prototyping
          p We help you validate your product concept before you build it.  Rapid prototyping with click-through designs will help us iterate on your idea to find both a viable solution and a validated product experience.  Our prototypes aim to align internal and external stakeholders, as well as collect feedback from potential early adopters. 
        .service-text-fixed#branding
          h1 Product Branding
          p Our designers will work with you to give your product a voice and style through product branding. A good brand informs product style, copy direction, and market position.  Your brand includes all of the touch points that a person has with your product or company.  You branding should be consistent across all mediums, and be unique to the personality and purpose of the solution. 
        .service-text-fixed#ux    
          h1 Early customer development
          p  We'll work to craft an experience that delights the user and enhances the value of the solution you are creating.  Our designers consider each feature's user interface, as well as the interactive moments that guide the person through the product.  Our aim is is delight users and provide them value.      
        //- new stuff add videos below
        .service-text-fixed#api    
          h1 Web application API development
          p  Our in-house development team will collaborate with strategy, design and you to create web a application that is ready to scale.  We use modern open source technology for API development in order to provide the most extensible platforms across devices and integrations.  
        .service-text-fixed#mobile    
          h1 Mobile and wearable development
          p  We build products for every screen.  Our in-house developers work to connect mobile platforms to serve people in ways unique to their mobile needs.  We build wearable apps to help make your product a part of the customer's daily life.  
        .service-text-fixed#test    
          h1 Usability testing
          p  We work with you to test the usability and overall concept of your product early and often.  We believe that our product assumptions must be validated with real people to make sure that the it provides the greatest possible value.  
        .service-text-fixed#product    
          h1 Product launch strategy
          p  We align product development and branding to the growth, PR, marketing, and sales aspects of your business.  Our team works with you to make sure that product and growth informing each other to move toward effective private and public releases.
        .service-text-fixed#early    
          h1 Early customer development
          p  When launching a new product, your early customers are the building blocks for success.  They are your sounding board and your ambassadors to jump-start the scaling process.  As a team we will engage and incentivize your early customers to gather feedback and spread the word about the solutions we are bringing to life.       
       

        
